#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom provider"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To develop a custom hostname provider you need to implement `org.keycloak."
"urls.HostnameProviderFactory` and `org.keycloak.urls.HostnameProvider`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Follow the instructions in the Service Provider Interfaces section in link:"
